Very quiet in here as we all wait for updates/new both in game and on forum, so I thought I would fill the silence with a few ideas for routes that had been running around my head.

Idea 1. Ballet/Dance Route
Fetishes: exhibitionism, bondage/BDSM, objectification, age difference, latex, prostitution
Ballet/Dance would be added as an option for characters with either petite or standard bodies. (A possibility of making your body flexible in initial choices could open up new stuff) It would be available at the Job/activity fair, and would be an option that your father approves of on that route. While training in such an art would usually require years of training from a young age, it is well in reason to say the X-change pill gives you the flexibility required.

I could see this route going potentially 3 ways. Providing of course the routes are pursued, similar to how the barista route can be casual employment or lead down the Andrew Path, army wife path etc.

a) Traditional route - the ballet/dance group would be run by Mr and Mrs Dance (no relation, insert east European names). If you follow Mr Dance's route you become a classically trained ballerina, and is the route to take if you want to avoid any sexual encounters that might interfere with routes outside of the activity.

b) Prima Ballerina route - Having taken Mr Dance's initial route, you will eventually hit upon a choice. The choice appearing could be whether you picked 'good student' in the beginning, or perhaps had the 'flexibility' perk if implemented. The choice Mr Dance will give you will be to continue dancing casually, or go into a more serious class if you want to pursue it as a career. The first choice would lead you down route a., the second would lead you down this storyline. Prima Ballerina would be a more serious and professional discipline, hence instead of holidays spent going to the beach with classmates, you would instead attend dance camps and go to performances. This route then splits into 4.
- Mr Dance is obviously attracted to you, despite being more than twice your age. However he is professional and will not make advances on you. Main Character (MC) could choose to start a relationship with him, but would require you to leave the dance program. Mr Dance is a very loving relationship despite the age difference, and you eventually become a dance instructor yourself and/or start a family with him - ENDING: Dance Teacher
- You eventually get close to a fellow dancer, and eventually become a duo together, both on stage and off. You both have long and successful careers, before settling down and starting a family if you so choose. - ENDING: Entwined
- If you do not get into a relationship, you rise through the ranks over the years, and eventually you star in a world-class performance in Paris. There, as you dazzle the crowd, you enrapture the eye of the Crown Prince of *insert country with monarchy*. He makes contact after the performance, and you start dating. After some time the King/Queen dies, and he ascends to the throne. He asks you to stay with him, and if you say yes, you marry and become Queen Consort. Unlike the Royal Concubine ending this would be a full on Royal Ending. It would end with you having kids and securing the future of his line. - ENDING: Royal Family
- The final ending would see no serious relationships chosen during your time as a dancer. You would rise through the ranks to be the best Prima Ballerina in the world, obtaining heights obtained by few before you, and becoming a household name across the globe. Eventually you make your final performance after a sold-out world tour, the story ends with the crowd standing and applauding both you and your career. - ENDING: Prima Ballerina

c) Burlesque route - This route requires you to continue under Mrs Dance's tutelage, and is the more fetishistic route to take. It would include venturing into the more risqué areas of dance, or perhaps quitting dance altogether and becoming a plaything for Mrs Dance and/or the wealthy of society. The route would start after accepting Mrs Dance's offer of 'alternative' dancing styles, which would begin a slow descent into depravity. This route should be quit-able until a certain point, after all Mrs Dance is not doing anything illegal and Mr Dance is aware that not everyone will be comfortable with her methods. This route would have 2 branches, one being larger than the other.
- Firstly would simply be the burlesque dance route. While you are wearing less on stage than perhaps a normal dancer would, what you are wearing is far more extravagant. This route would not have an ending, rather an achievement and would eventually end back onto the main storyline.
- The second route requires you to accept Mrs Dance offer of quitting the main groups and joining her own private company. Whether she is truthful about it or not, this company very much consists or 18+ performances, including but not limited to sex on stage, dancing in bondage, and any props being people in tied positions.
- You very much catch the eye of Mrs Dance, especially when you are performing in bondage or as a piece of furniture. Mrs Dance offers you a place by her side, but it is not an equal relationship. You are instead instructed to wear full latex and act as her personal servant/maid/slave/chair. If you wanted to get dark she does not have any true feelings for you besides lust, and you are simply added to the collection of other dancers constricted in her house. - ENDING: Spider and the Fly
- If you decline the offer, you continue as a burlesque dancer, but stumble upon another way Mrs Dance makes money; selling her dancers to clients. Never a permanent deal, it could be for as little as an hour, or as long as a fortnight if they are hosting an event. Eventually you settle, or even embrace the lifestyle. - ENDING: Black Swan


That was longer than I expected, anyways onto next idea

Idea 2. Farmhand Route
Fetishes: Pregnancy, lactation, expansion, Hucow, incest?, is being a housewife a fetish?, maid, petplay, brainwashing

Two ways this route could come about. Firstly it could be a job/activity, similar to my idea for ballet/dance. This would require longer trips, and would take up holiday time. My second idea for implementing this route would be upon the selection of the agriculture major, which mentions your grandfather owning a farm, but doesn't go anywhere. Personally I am more a fan of the agriculture major path, as it adds some later came content and doesn't cluster the opening job options.
I do not think this route should be as big as my proposed dance route. It would be a job that runs beside the main storyline and leads to a few bad ends if you make the 'wrong' choices. If you graduate with the major you'll take over your grandfathers farm and would lead to a few more endings.

a) Graduation route - Requires graduating in agriculture, as well as not being in a restrictive relationship and/or pregnant (think Andrew, woman in the Bar, Barry etc.). Upon graduation you would start a job as a farmhand underneath your grandfather, with the agreement being that if you can help him run the farm satisfactorily, he will hand over the reigns to you. This route would have 3 branches all with their own ending.
- If you are in a relationship, and your partner offers you their help on the farm, you both move onto the property. Eventually your grandfather hands over the property and retires, with you and your now husband/wife taking over and starting a family. - ENDING: Big Sky Country
- If you are not in a relationship, you still take over the farm, although your grandfather stays on a bit longer. Eventually he offers for one of your cousins to come out and help, as they've expressed interest in the past. If you decline he accepts your choice, and you start running the farm by yourself. - ENDING: Farmer wants a wife (aussie tv show)
- If you do accept your grandfather's offer, he gives you two choices depending on gender preference. Your cousin arrives and is very friendly, helping around the farm. However over time they become more domineering, and start restricting you to more household chores as well as beginning a relationship with you. Your grandfather passes on the farm but to them instead of you. - ENDING: Farmer's wife (cousin can be changed to friend of the family if you want to steer away from cousin relationship)

b) In service to the farm route - achieved by helping out on the farm before the graduation. This route requires you stuffing up on the farm in some way or another, and in so doing requires you to drop out of school and fix your mistakes.
- Hucow path aka. human developing cow-like aspects like excessive lactation and/or transformation. Achieved two possible ways. First is over times working at the farm your grandfather brings up an experimental new feed for his cows that may boost milk production. It seems to succeed. Eventually your grandfather leaves you in charge of the farm for the weekend as he is visiting family. While feeding the cows on the Friday night, you discover one of the milking machines is broken. If you attempt to fix it yourself instead of calling someone, it senses a 'cow' and restrains you, beginning to force feed you the mixture. Come Sunday afternoon you are found by your grandfather, but by then your breasts have swelled and lactating heavily. While he does unhook you, eventually you both realize the state of the changes and you go back (happily?) to the machine. - ENDING: Hooked up
- alternatively you could try the feed over time, producing a slow transformation.
- alternatively if you are seeking a bad end, the feed could produce further side effect, reducing intelligence to a point where your grandfather keeps you hooked up.
- After working on the farm you accidentally start a fire, if MC makes the wrong choices you cause a significant amount of damage, and cause your grandfather to lose a lot of money. Furious, your grandfather drags you to the Uni offices, and demanding compensation for what he calls the fault of the X-Change pill. The uni offers two alternative solutions.
- Firstly they offer a pill that would make you docile and hardworking, a perfect farmhand/maid/servant. This would make his life easier so he could focus on repairing. If this path is chosen MC thinks of nothing but helping on the farm, and when he hands the reigns over to someone else you become the servant of them. - ENDING: drone
- Secondly they offer an alternative pill, which would change your physiology to replace the cow killed in the fire. This is the second route for hucow. However this pill changes you far more, reducing intellect, changing voicebox to only produce moos, growing the start of horns and weakening your legs to the point of crawling everywhere. You become the best producing 'cow' on the farm, and your milk becomes famous (although no one knows its true source). Seeing an opportunity your grandfather doesn't change you back. - ENDING: Moo?

