My ideas for future storylines.

Father expansion. The new father choice at the start opens up some potential new avenues. Obviously your father has a conservative way of seeing women and their role in the relationship; with women being submissive to their husbands and obeying them. I think it would be interesting to see him take this further. Ideas like the following

- Instead of the chaste wife ending, a graduating player who is a) single and b) went with his choices, is 'auctioned' off by your father in an arranged marriage, one that he approves of. I believe this would work best if there are further choices for your life that he suggests, and if you follow them leads down this path. E.g. what your major is, sorority choices, even roommates.

- It's noted that your sister has issues with your father. Perhaps in the future your father tricks or coerces your sister into taking an X-change pill that keeps her female but makes her submissive and obedient, this could expand to the brother and even mother as well.

- Finally could be a branch of the chaste wife storyline. If your character has had sex with the brother and/or uncle, you can have sex with your father and begin a secret relationship.

I don't think your father has sinister intentions at the start, but I feel if the right choices (or wrong choices) are made, the power he has over his family could go to his head, and he could have a stepford wives/handmaid's tale future. (I know the former is technically already in game). Perhaps he suggests an ultra-conservative club for you to join, which shares his views on women. Maybe he does/doesn't realize how traditionalist they actually are.


**Me** Most likely one to implement:
In relation to the father storyline, I wish the Uncle storyline could be slowed down a bit and/or expanded upon. My idea for this would be he opens your submissiveness to him slowly, starting with 'innocent' acts of obedience but eventually exacting more and more control over you. Perhaps he asks you to fetch him a drink first, then makes you wear the ex's clothes, until eventually perhaps over several holidays you become a willing slave. Of course the current way should be kept in, just an alternate route.
Also I hope it gets implemented that there is a way to submit to him without your brother f***ing you.


**Me** Maybe:
A sub-branch of the concubine route that ends up with you marrying into royalty and becoming Princess/Queen. Doesn't have to be the prince in game, maybe you meet a prince from a far-away kingdom and really hit it off? Then do you continue your relationship with this new prince, or go after the older but more powerful widowed king? A route that ends with real power would be interesting in my opinion.

A ballet club or dance club would be interesting, as another choice for first jobs. Ballet dancing is high intensity with pressure both from on and off the stage, take the chance to be a white, pure swan, or succumb to your desires and embody the black swan.

Finally would be a branch at the end of the obedient wife, perhaps on the bdsm island, that ends up with you and Andrew having a poly relationship, with him having 2 sub wives. Unlike the other poly ending this is still a really loving marriage, not just built around sex. If not poly perhaps obedience is taken further, ending up closer to a maid/slave than a wife.

Still, whatever future routes and ending you have planned, I am eagerly looking forward to them. (and if you want to ask questions about my ideas I am happy to answer and stretch them out)
